{"id": "1412427624491389079", "channel_id": "1412427624491389079", "type": 0, "author_id": "498141099336925186", "author_name": "b3po.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello, i'm new to the game and was wondering if this is a good team for helot, also, idk what wod are good for hameln and thais, i used the recommended button on them.", "timestamp": "2025-09-02T13:23:07.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1412427625233911849", "filename": "Screenshot_20250902_151914_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 120530, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412427624491389079/1412427625233911849/Screenshot_20250902_151914_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cd1c3b&is=69cbcabb&hm=dd8265cacca3bea617c4231db131bac6d61365ef594f3610be47fee8f2f7f012&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412427624491389079", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with catena team and wods.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1412431205508321280", "channel_id": "1412427624491389079", "type": 19, "author_id": "523092262465306626", "author_name": "farr8506", "author_bot": false, "content": "yes this is a good team, when you finish chapter 7 youd want to change your posse into lone seed. i also suggest that you start wheel jail, get the blade of titan towards +12 so you could slot it on ghelot alongside her sig and use a prototype dupe on thais to get her e2. for covenants its april for ghelot as with most dps's (the chapter 8 covenant), and life drain on either hameln or thais or even aigis (post ch 7 conv)", "timestamp": "2025-09-02T13:37:21.096000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["498141099336925186"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1412427624491389079", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412427624491389079", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with catena team and wods.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
