{"id": "1412443127830286407", "channel_id": "1412427624491389079", "type": 19, "author_id": "523092262465306626", "author_name": "farr8506", "author_bot": false, "content": "use these 3 wheels, you can put two of them on hameln and the last one on aigis. in arc 1 (the first 9 chapters of the main story) the left one allows you to refresh the shop three times and with only 5 sigil cost, the middle one allows you to buy cursed relics which most of them are pretty busted, and the right one allows you to increase max hp instead of picking an orison after battle. combine these three and they're probably the most optimal wheels to run in arc 1", "timestamp": "2025-09-02T14:24:43.599000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-02T14:25:53.779000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["498141099336925186"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1412443127515578430", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 53004, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412427624491389079/1412443127515578430/image.png?ex=69cd2aab&is=69cbd92b&hm=d125c02fb25604154402164de3748035e05a90a2adb98ca83294046687ef0177&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1412441107756748821", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412427624491389079", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Help with catena team and wods.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
